snippet: World number one Serena Williams set up a rematch of last year's Australian Open final against Maria Sharapova after she comfortably accounted for Russian Margarita Gasparyan 6-2 6-1 in the fourth round on Sunday....
lead_paragraph: World number one Serena Williams set up a rematch of last year's Australian Open final against Maria Sharapova after she comfortably accounted for Russian Margarita Gasparyan 6-2 6-1 in the fourth round on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Swift Serena Into Australian Open Quarter-Finals
headline.main: Swift Serena Into Australian Open Quarter-Finals
